Syria to Issue New Law on Free Zone Investments, Baath Says

-- B y   L i n a   I b r a h i m
-- 
2011-03-01T08:41:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-06/syria-turkey-start-dam-at-border-of-countries-agency-reports.html
The Syrian government will issue
“within days” a new law to reorganize investments in the
country’s free zones, Baath newspaper said, citing an
unidentified official working in the free zones.  Trading activities in the free zones declined 40 percent in
2010, the Damascus-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lina Ibrahim in Dubai at  librahim4@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss at   sev@bloomberg.net  